body:
Infinity War theory

Okay so we all know that Thanos halved the universe at the end of Infinity War but he literally halved the universe. Every relationship which meant a lot to the characters (their other halves (not necessarily romantically)) have been split up at the end of Infinity War. Like Steve and Bucky, Peter and Tony etc etc. Therefore our buddy Thanos was arguably punishing the avengers for trying to stop him from halving the universe. Therefore Thanos is a douche. Thanks for coming to my TedTalk
